snippet.title: A Mausoleum for All (Gameplay Trailer)
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2631270/A_Mausoleum_for_All/

Wishlist the game on Steam!

You’ve been sealed up in a derelict restaurant with no escape, but you’re not alone. Your family has been interred with you, but they’ve changed, and they’re eager to free you of that needless flesh.
